{"tid":1379591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急注意今次生死存亡之關鍵","createTime":"2019-07-28T21:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T22:04:16.000Z","uid":293049,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"33a56386de2ac6c36ad26f02c2637fbd7e0aebc3","tid":1379591,"uid":293049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:18:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最近幾次活動，<br />\n越來越多不明人仕偽裝抗爭者，<br />\n但不斷勸退後勤巴絲，令前線義士冇晒後援，無奈地撤退。<br />\n近幾次觀察所得，佢哋有組織，有團隊，裝束係Full gear 扮前線抗爭者，但只游走後援地區，成撚日話前線有共識啦，扮前線代言人，制造假消息。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1)  乜撚嘢1125一齊走，730一齊走，(前線根本冇可能咁早會話走)<br />\n2)  而家有車，要走而家好走啦。(嚇鳩人遲D冇車走，要盡快走)<br />\n3)  保持實力，Be Water， 下次再嚟。<br />\n4)  唔洗買票，地鐵開咗閘啦，快D入閘啦。(不斷催人走)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">最撚過份係元朗嗰日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n一班後勤巴絲喺元朗站朗日街天橋上為前線打氣助攻，有個仆街冚家鏟，用唔好阻塞通道為藉口(當時同黑警對侍嘅義士已經唔多，天橋好闊，企兩行人都仲有好闊路可行)，不斷推走天橋上嘅助攻者，<br />\n有個義士用電筒射狗同屌狗，個仆街就屌鳩個義士，叫佢唔好挑釁D狗。<br />\n依個撚屌根本想推走晒橋上嘅助攻者，<br />\n令前線義士覺得冇晒後援，不得不撤。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">依班仆街不斷勸退後勤，令前線冇支持，無奈撒退。</span><br />\n如果再畀依D假扮抗爭者，繼續不斷拖大家後腳，之後嘅發展，就會畀依D仆街冚家鏟拖誇。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">注意</span></span></span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">以後發現依D人，大家一定要圍佢，叫佢表明身份，質問佢吹假風目的為何。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請廣傳留意</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>強烈譴責依D卑鄙無恥行為。</ins></span></span>"},{"pid":"e5b1e1450ff5bf04812fc721c692d34d42813213","tid":1379591,"uid":249187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:20:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39093d2755022fa05f6143c49910d8f766a38ef6","tid":1379591,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:21:27.000Z","msg":"係前線亂9咁屌人只會造成分化"},{"pid":"38db41783a6f4bc2087c78cd330f7f5106227cde","tid":1379591,"uid":64946,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:23:20.000Z","msg":"P 牌post 開完有P牌即刻推 大家睇路啦 <br />\n唔好再留comment 幫佢推post <br />\n分化撚confirmed"},{"pid":"4398c3fccf5a779c5a7d61c6b29244a383b960b4","tid":1379591,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33a56386de2ac6c36ad26f02c2637fbd7e0aebc3","tid":1379591,"uid":293049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:18:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最近幾次活動，<br />\n越來越多不明人仕偽裝抗爭者，<br />\n但不斷勸退後勤巴絲，令前線義士冇晒後援，無奈地撤退。<br />\n近幾次觀察所得，佢哋有組織，有團隊，裝束係Full gear 扮前線抗爭者，但只游走後援地區，成撚日話前線有共識啦，扮前線代言人，制造假消息。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1)  乜撚嘢1125一齊走，730一齊走，(前線根本冇可能咁早會話走)<br />\n2)  而家有車，要走而家好走啦。(嚇鳩人遲D冇車走，要盡快走)<br />\n3)  保持實力，Be Water， 下次再嚟。<br />\n4)  唔洗買票，地鐵開咗閘啦，快D入閘啦。(不斷催人走)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">最撚過份係元朗嗰日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/